This paper discusses the development of context-aware NMT systems, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning (ML). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of metrics and models, which are common topics in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of larger amounts of data, which is relevant to the sub-categories of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
